1
00:00:08,420 --> 00:00:10,820
♪Let me write the legend♪

2
00:00:10,820 --> 00:00:13,580
=Young Swordsman=

3
00:00:13,580 --> 00:00:16,580
=Episode 6=

4
00:00:19,480 --> 00:00:20,160
Master.

5
00:00:20,199 --> 00:00:21,640
How's the pressure?

6
00:00:21,640 --> 00:00:22,480
Not bad.

7
00:00:23,120 --> 00:00:23,839
A little to the right.

8
00:00:24,079 --> 00:00:24,839
Yeah, yeah.

9
00:00:25,440 --> 00:00:26,160
Right there.

10
00:00:26,800 --> 00:00:28,039
Wait...

11
00:00:28,039 --> 00:00:30,920
You're saying he's Tang Changsheng,

12
00:00:30,960 --> 00:00:31,920
the famous master of Tang Clan?

13
00:00:32,600 --> 00:00:35,000
Please, miss, you flatter me.

14
00:00:35,039 --> 00:00:36,240
With my master right here,

15
00:00:36,240 --> 00:00:38,359
how could I put on airs?

16
00:00:38,679 --> 00:00:40,079
What? He's your disciple?

17
00:00:41,719 --> 00:00:43,520
To be precise,

18
00:00:43,520 --> 00:00:45,799
Changsheng was the first disciple
I ever took.

19
00:00:46,679 --> 00:00:49,000
Master, I don't deserve such honor.

20
00:00:49,840 --> 00:00:51,240
But everyone says
the master of Tang Clan

21
00:00:51,240 --> 00:00:53,759
renounced worldly life five years ago.

22
00:00:53,759 --> 00:00:54,920
He buried his sword in a secluded valley

23
00:00:55,039 --> 00:00:56,320
and has roamed the land ever since,

24
00:00:56,320 --> 00:00:57,560
healing the sick.

25
00:00:57,600 --> 00:00:59,200
They call him the Divine Healer.

26
00:00:59,240 --> 00:01:00,039
He...

27
00:01:00,880 --> 00:01:02,439
He's your disciple?

28
00:01:03,640 --> 00:01:05,079
What if I told you

29
00:01:06,040 --> 00:01:07,680
I taught him everything

30
00:01:09,599 --> 00:01:11,200
he knows about medicine?

31
00:01:18,079 --> 00:01:19,239
Oh, no!

32
00:01:19,480 --> 00:01:21,719
These three needles

33
00:01:21,719 --> 00:01:23,560
should've cleared his meridians.

34
00:01:23,680 --> 00:01:24,120
But

35
00:01:24,200 --> 00:01:26,680
why isn't he responding?

36
00:01:27,079 --> 00:01:27,560
Strange.

37
00:01:27,560 --> 00:01:30,120
Old man, his lung meridian
is completely blocked,

38
00:01:30,120 --> 00:01:31,359
and you're needling
the Shanzhong acupoint?

39
00:01:31,359 --> 00:01:32,760
That'll only force
the phlegm into his lungs.

40
00:01:32,959 --> 00:01:34,000
Needle the Tiantu acupoint instead.

41
00:01:34,000 --> 00:01:36,200
Then prick the bruising at
Zhongfu acupoint with a silver needle.

42
00:01:36,200 --> 00:01:37,120
Try that.

43
00:01:51,239 --> 00:01:52,120
That's incredible!

44
00:01:53,359 --> 00:01:54,599
Young man, wait!

45
00:01:54,599 --> 00:01:55,159
Young man!

46
00:01:55,599 --> 00:01:56,879
You're so young,

47
00:01:56,879 --> 00:01:58,480
yet your medical skills are remarkable.

48
00:01:58,599 --> 00:02:00,439
I'm Tang Changsheng.

49
00:02:00,480 --> 00:02:02,840
May I ask your name?

50
00:02:02,959 --> 00:02:03,680
Peng Dasheng.

51
00:02:04,120 --> 00:02:05,640
Those were just a few family techniques.

52
00:02:05,640 --> 00:02:06,680
I wouldn't call that
much of a medical skill.

53
00:02:06,959 --> 00:02:07,840
Mr. Peng,

54
00:02:07,840 --> 00:02:09,240
you're far too modest.

55
00:02:09,240 --> 00:02:10,680
What you said just now

56
00:02:10,680 --> 00:02:12,800
cleared everything up for me.

57
00:02:12,800 --> 00:02:15,639
I learned more from you
than I have in ten years of study.

58
00:02:15,879 --> 00:02:17,199
If you'll have me,

59
00:02:17,199 --> 00:02:18,319
please take me as your disciple

60
00:02:18,319 --> 00:02:19,800
and teach me medicine.

61
00:02:19,800 --> 00:02:21,319
You want me to be your master?

62
00:02:22,680 --> 00:02:23,680
Master,

63
00:02:23,680 --> 00:02:25,919
please accept my bow.

64
00:02:29,719 --> 00:02:30,520
Master,

65
00:02:31,039 --> 00:02:32,280
I'm a slow learner.

66
00:02:32,360 --> 00:02:34,479
Of the Guigu Divine Needles
you taught me,

67
00:02:34,479 --> 00:02:35,439
I've only grasped

68
00:02:35,439 --> 00:02:38,520
sixty or seventy percent.

69
00:02:39,000 --> 00:02:40,840
That's because you never study hard.

70
00:02:42,719 --> 00:02:43,120
By the way,

71
00:02:43,159 --> 00:02:44,919
how did you know Xiaojiu was in danger?

72
00:02:47,840 --> 00:02:49,919
Well, Master...

73
00:02:49,960 --> 00:02:51,400
Here's what you don't know.

74
00:02:51,400 --> 00:02:53,719
I often travel
through the martial world.

75
00:02:53,719 --> 00:02:56,319
To avoid unnecessary trouble,

76
00:02:56,319 --> 00:02:59,400
I usually travel in disguise.

77
00:02:59,560 --> 00:03:00,240
Today,

78
00:03:00,240 --> 00:03:02,120
I happened to pass through Gusu

79
00:03:02,280 --> 00:03:03,599
and ran into you

80
00:03:03,599 --> 00:03:05,199
and this young lady.

81
00:03:14,599 --> 00:03:16,479
Oh, I remember now.

82
00:03:16,520 --> 00:03:18,479
You're that fortune-teller!

83
00:03:19,639 --> 00:03:21,159
Good eye, miss.

84
00:03:21,680 --> 00:03:23,159
The martial world is a dangerous place,

85
00:03:23,159 --> 00:03:24,719
and the Demon Sect is running rampant.

86
00:03:24,759 --> 00:03:25,800
Master, I was worried

87
00:03:25,800 --> 00:03:27,159
someone might plot against you,

88
00:03:27,159 --> 00:03:28,080
so I secretly

89
00:03:28,080 --> 00:03:30,800
followed you here.

90
00:03:31,400 --> 00:03:32,639
That old scoundrel

91
00:03:32,639 --> 00:03:34,360
Murong Xiang,

92
00:03:34,360 --> 00:03:36,319
broke off the engagement

93
00:03:36,319 --> 00:03:37,719
just to chase wealth and status,

94
00:03:37,719 --> 00:03:39,479
then insulted you on top of it.

95
00:03:39,479 --> 00:03:41,599
I can't let that slide.

96
00:03:41,599 --> 00:03:43,240
Just give the word, Master.

97
00:03:43,240 --> 00:03:44,960
I'll rally Tang Sect

98
00:03:44,960 --> 00:03:46,240
and force him to give in.

99
00:03:46,400 --> 00:03:47,199
No need.

100
00:03:48,360 --> 00:03:49,719
I'll settle things

101
00:03:50,240 --> 00:03:51,560
with the Murong Manor myself.

102
00:03:52,240 --> 00:03:53,120
All right.

103
00:03:55,479 --> 00:03:57,319
Still, it's a good thing
you arrived when you did.

104
00:03:57,759 --> 00:03:59,000
Otherwise, Xiaojiu
would've been in real danger.

105
00:03:59,560 --> 00:04:00,159
Master,

106
00:04:00,159 --> 00:04:01,520
I hardly did anything.

107
00:04:02,000 --> 00:04:04,159
It was the Tianji Armor

108
00:04:04,159 --> 00:04:06,120
Miss Fang was wearing
that protected her.

109
00:04:06,120 --> 00:04:07,840
Fortune was on her side.

110
00:04:18,879 --> 00:04:21,199
Master, what do we do with him?

111
00:04:29,839 --> 00:04:30,959
You useless fool!

112
00:04:31,199 --> 00:04:31,879
I'm warning you.

113
00:04:31,879 --> 00:04:33,240
Let me go right now!

114
00:04:33,560 --> 00:04:35,560
When my fellows
from the Sihai Gang get here,

115
00:04:35,839 --> 00:04:38,120
every last one of you

116
00:04:38,120 --> 00:04:39,319
will die!

117
00:04:41,600 --> 00:04:43,519
You dare hit me?

118
00:04:46,519 --> 00:04:48,720
You've got a death wish!

119
00:04:48,920 --> 00:04:51,920
Do you know what happens
when you cross Sihai Gang?

120
00:04:54,879 --> 00:04:56,959
Sihai Gang? You're nothing.

121
00:04:58,079 --> 00:04:59,399
Listen carefully.

122
00:04:59,560 --> 00:05:02,199
Sihai Gang is the biggest gang in Gusu.

123
00:05:02,279 --> 00:05:05,040
Even the Liushan Sect
has to show us respect.

124
00:05:06,160 --> 00:05:08,360
I thought you were
some kind of big shot.

125
00:05:08,360 --> 00:05:10,279
Turns out you're just
a bunch of street thugs.

126
00:05:10,519 --> 00:05:12,600
Spit it out. Who sent you?

127
00:05:12,839 --> 00:05:14,879
The name alone will scare you senseless.

128
00:05:15,000 --> 00:05:15,720
My master

129
00:05:15,720 --> 00:05:18,560
is Lin Dun,

130
00:05:18,560 --> 00:05:19,600
the heir of Huxiao Manor in Gusu.

131
00:05:22,240 --> 00:05:24,240
Dasheng, this man is ruthless.

132
00:05:24,240 --> 00:05:25,160
He's clearly done this before.

133
00:05:25,160 --> 00:05:26,480
We can't let him off easily.

134
00:05:27,959 --> 00:05:28,800
Tell me.

135
00:05:29,040 --> 00:05:31,319
How many times have you done this?

136
00:05:31,439 --> 00:05:32,040
What a joke.

137
00:05:32,439 --> 00:05:34,839
Ask anyone in Gusu.

138
00:05:34,879 --> 00:05:37,160
Everyone knows Wang Yang of Sihai Gang.

139
00:05:37,560 --> 00:05:39,879
If a woman catches my eye,
her family sends her

140
00:05:40,000 --> 00:05:42,759
straight to my bed. No one dares refuse.

141
00:05:43,040 --> 00:05:44,199
Listen.

142
00:05:44,480 --> 00:05:45,639
If I'm not back

143
00:05:45,639 --> 00:05:47,079
within two hours,

144
00:05:47,079 --> 00:05:48,920
my fellows from Sihai Gang

145
00:05:48,920 --> 00:05:50,920
will surround this place,

146
00:05:50,920 --> 00:05:52,079
so no one can get in or out. And then...

147
00:06:00,320 --> 00:06:01,560
(Zhenming Hall)

148
00:06:04,980 --> 00:06:08,920
(Sihai Gang)

149
00:06:08,920 --> 00:06:10,079
Come on!

150
00:06:10,079 --> 00:06:10,480
Drink up!

151
00:06:10,519 --> 00:06:11,879
Five!

152
00:06:11,879 --> 00:06:13,079
Eight!

153
00:06:17,120 --> 00:06:17,959
First Chief...

154
00:06:23,040 --> 00:06:23,839
Who are you?

155
00:06:24,040 --> 00:06:25,480
Wuhuduandao Sect,

156
00:06:25,759 --> 00:06:26,920
Peng Dasheng.

157
00:06:27,160 --> 00:06:29,560
You came alone
to raid a Sihai Gang stronghold?

158
00:06:29,600 --> 00:06:30,680
Got a death wish?

159
00:06:34,519 --> 00:06:35,759
Is this everyone?

160
00:06:37,560 --> 00:06:38,800
You're asking for it.

161
00:06:40,040 --> 00:06:40,720
Get him!

162
00:06:45,100 --> 00:06:46,700
♪This battle, I won't retreat♪

163
00:06:48,700 --> 00:06:50,260
♪I emerge into the world♪

164
00:06:50,260 --> 00:06:52,020
♪Unknown, yet I dare
to shake the martial world♪

165
00:06:52,020 --> 00:06:53,380
♪My pride is my trump card♪

166
00:06:53,380 --> 00:06:55,180
♪Even if fate treats me as worthless,
I refuse to yield♪

167
00:06:55,180 --> 00:06:56,580
♪Born with a gift, I won't give in♪

168
00:06:56,580 --> 00:06:58,340
♪Against heaven's will,
I'll bet on my rise♪

169
00:06:58,340 --> 00:06:59,860
♪A sword in hand,
fresh out of the mountain♪

170
00:06:59,860 --> 00:07:01,580
♪I dare to break every rule♪

171
00:07:01,580 --> 00:07:02,900
♪I see through
the masks of human hearts♪

172
00:07:02,900 --> 00:07:04,740
♪Famous clans are nothing
but a few layers of disguise♪

173
00:07:04,740 --> 00:07:05,980
♪They kneel and beg for fame♪

174
00:07:05,980 --> 00:07:08,220
♪I stand and fight for my dignity♪

175
00:07:08,220 --> 00:07:09,740
♪Facing powerful foes, I will not bow♪

176
00:07:09,740 --> 00:07:11,340
♪With my blade in hand,
I decide what is right♪

177
00:07:11,340 --> 00:07:12,940
♪Stand for justice and never step back♪

178
00:07:12,940 --> 00:07:14,420
♪Even if the whole world
stands against me♪

179
00:07:14,420 --> 00:07:16,700
♪I rise against fate and fight♪

180
00:07:16,700 --> 00:07:19,140
♪My blood runs hot, my heart runs wild♪

181
00:07:19,260 --> 00:07:22,500
♪I won't live for someone else's glory♪

182
00:07:22,540 --> 00:07:26,740
♪I only want to shine
with a light of my own♪

183
00:07:27,120 --> 00:07:28,199
As of today,

184
00:07:28,639 --> 00:07:29,680
Sihai Gang

185
00:07:30,120 --> 00:07:31,120
is finished.

186
00:07:32,279 --> 00:07:34,399
I miss my mother.

187
00:07:34,959 --> 00:07:36,079
(Gusu County Office)
O-Officer...

188
00:07:36,680 --> 00:07:37,480
Officer!

189
00:07:37,759 --> 00:07:38,560
Officer!

190
00:07:40,040 --> 00:07:40,839
Officer!

191
00:07:41,959 --> 00:07:42,759
Officer!

192
00:07:43,120 --> 00:07:44,000
I'm here to turn myself in!

193
00:07:44,199 --> 00:07:46,759
Officer, I wanna go home!

194
00:07:47,519 --> 00:07:48,560
You're saying

195
00:07:48,639 --> 00:07:49,839
he took down Sihai Gang single-handedly,

196
00:07:49,839 --> 00:07:51,439
wrecked their stronghold,

197
00:07:51,639 --> 00:07:53,519
and handed them all
over to the authorities?

198
00:07:54,120 --> 00:07:55,639
Sihai Gang has spent years

199
00:07:55,680 --> 00:07:57,040
abducting women, robbing people,

200
00:07:57,040 --> 00:07:58,160
and terrorizing Gusu.

201
00:07:58,240 --> 00:08:00,319
They got off easy with just a beating.

202
00:08:02,519 --> 00:08:03,560
Interesting.

203
00:08:03,839 --> 00:08:06,199
Peng Dasheng has only
been in Gusu for one day,

204
00:08:06,199 --> 00:08:07,800
and he's already turned
the whole city upside down.

205
00:08:08,480 --> 00:08:10,519
The more I hear, the more I like him.

206
00:08:12,399 --> 00:08:13,199
Miss, you're determined

207
00:08:13,800 --> 00:08:16,680
to recruit Peng Dasheng, aren't you?

208
00:08:18,360 --> 00:08:19,560
Don't you think

209
00:08:19,600 --> 00:08:20,600
he's far more interesting

210
00:08:20,600 --> 00:08:22,959
than those martial clan heirs

211
00:08:23,199 --> 00:08:24,319
who only care about fame?

212
00:08:25,240 --> 00:08:27,839
But he comes from that... what was it?

213
00:08:27,839 --> 00:08:29,680
Wuhuduandao Sect?

214
00:08:30,160 --> 00:08:32,639
It's a tiny sect no one's ever heard of.

215
00:08:32,720 --> 00:08:34,679
Hardly worth mentioning.

216
00:08:35,080 --> 00:08:36,519
Not necessarily.

217
00:08:38,420 --> 00:08:43,340
(Wu Yangzi,
Grandmaster of the Wudu Sect)

218
00:08:59,559 --> 00:09:01,120
Master?

219
00:09:02,120 --> 00:09:03,360
What happened to you?

220
00:09:04,120 --> 00:09:06,159
I had a minor setback while cultivating

221
00:09:06,159 --> 00:09:07,679
the Formless Divine Art in seclusion.

222
00:09:07,679 --> 00:09:08,559
It's nothing serious.

223
00:09:08,840 --> 00:09:09,559
By the way,

224
00:09:10,120 --> 00:09:12,519
you said Peng Dasheng

225
00:09:12,519 --> 00:09:14,360
comes from the Wuhuduandao Sect?

226
00:09:14,840 --> 00:09:15,519
That's right.

227
00:09:15,919 --> 00:09:17,559
Master, you've heard of it?

228
00:09:18,279 --> 00:09:21,440
Very few people in the martial world

229
00:09:21,519 --> 00:09:23,399
even know that sect exists.

230
00:09:23,559 --> 00:09:26,240
If my master hadn't told me about it,

231
00:09:26,240 --> 00:09:28,799
I wouldn't know either.

232
00:09:29,000 --> 00:09:32,559
Years ago, there was a mysterious
saberman named Peng.

233
00:09:32,919 --> 00:09:35,200
His martial arts were extraordinary.

234
00:09:35,240 --> 00:09:38,039
He defeated the heads
of all Eight Great Sects.

235
00:09:38,159 --> 00:09:40,320
To win public support,

236
00:09:40,320 --> 00:09:42,320
the major sects
falsely branded him a villain

237
00:09:42,360 --> 00:09:44,799
and called on martial artists
across the land to hunt him down.

238
00:09:45,559 --> 00:09:47,120
He was highly skilled,

239
00:09:47,559 --> 00:09:49,559
but he had no sect behind him.

240
00:09:49,639 --> 00:09:51,919
In the end, his home was destroyed,
and his family was killed.

241
00:09:54,240 --> 00:09:56,080
After losing his loved ones,

242
00:09:56,080 --> 00:09:57,600
he retreated deep into the mountains.

243
00:09:57,600 --> 00:09:58,919
Then he devoted himself to the Dao,

244
00:09:58,919 --> 00:10:00,879
and vanished from the martial world.

245
00:10:01,159 --> 00:10:01,879
Legend says

246
00:10:01,879 --> 00:10:03,120
that atop Wuhu Mountain,

247
00:10:03,120 --> 00:10:05,200
he fully grasped
the balance of yin and yang.

248
00:10:05,519 --> 00:10:08,000
He combined the martial arts
of countless schools

249
00:10:08,000 --> 00:10:09,480
with Daoist breathing techniques

250
00:10:09,559 --> 00:10:11,919
and created the Wuhuduandao Sect.

251
00:10:12,080 --> 00:10:13,320
He spent the rest of his life there

252
00:10:13,320 --> 00:10:15,080
and never came down the mountain again.

253
00:10:16,080 --> 00:10:18,559
No wonder his fighting style

254
00:10:18,679 --> 00:10:20,080
is so unpredictable.

255
00:10:20,600 --> 00:10:22,200
He takes the best from every school

256
00:10:22,200 --> 00:10:23,240
and makes it his own.

257
00:10:23,480 --> 00:10:25,320
If we can bring him over to our side,

258
00:10:25,320 --> 00:10:27,720
or gain the support
of the Wuhuduandao Sect,

259
00:10:28,159 --> 00:10:29,240
the Demon Sect

260
00:10:29,519 --> 00:10:30,879
will surely fall in time.

261
00:10:31,960 --> 00:10:32,960
I understand, Master.

262
00:10:34,440 --> 00:10:35,279
I heard Peng Dasheng

263
00:10:35,360 --> 00:10:37,600
plans to enter
Murong Manor's martial tournament.

264
00:10:37,679 --> 00:10:40,440
Let's use this opportunity
to give him a hand.

265
00:10:43,120 --> 00:10:43,799
Send word.

266
00:10:44,279 --> 00:10:46,240
Summon the leaders of Miaojiang's
Thirty-Six Caves

267
00:10:46,240 --> 00:10:47,320
and have them gather in Gusu.

268
00:10:47,720 --> 00:10:50,919
I've got a grand gift for Peng Dasheng.

269
00:10:51,420 --> 00:10:55,340
(Yaowang Residence)

270
00:10:55,759 --> 00:10:56,960
Yaowang Residence

271
00:10:56,960 --> 00:10:58,919
hasn't been renovated in years,

272
00:10:58,919 --> 00:11:00,519
but at least it's quiet here.

273
00:11:00,600 --> 00:11:02,919
Master, while you and Miss Fang

274
00:11:02,919 --> 00:11:04,840
are lying low in Gusu,

275
00:11:04,879 --> 00:11:06,759
you might as well stay here.

276
00:11:07,360 --> 00:11:10,519
Mr. Tang, do you have a shrine here?

277
00:11:10,639 --> 00:11:11,399
Of course.

278
00:11:11,399 --> 00:11:12,759
There's a statue of Shennong inside.

279
00:11:12,799 --> 00:11:13,919
They say it works miracles.

280
00:11:13,919 --> 00:11:15,240
Prayers here are always answered.

281
00:11:17,240 --> 00:11:19,240
Since I had to flee my home,

282
00:11:19,600 --> 00:11:22,000
I haven't set up an altar
to honor my father.

283
00:11:22,600 --> 00:11:23,639
Dasheng,

284
00:11:23,720 --> 00:11:26,159
I'd like to go pay my respects.

285
00:11:26,840 --> 00:11:27,639
All right.

286
00:11:36,440 --> 00:11:37,639
M-Master...

287
00:11:38,200 --> 00:11:41,360
What's going on between you and Xiaojiu?

288
00:11:44,159 --> 00:11:45,559
We met by chance.

289
00:11:46,120 --> 00:11:46,559
By chance?

290
00:11:46,559 --> 00:11:48,519
She was all alone and being hunted down.

291
00:11:48,519 --> 00:11:48,840
I...

292
00:11:48,840 --> 00:11:50,279
How could I just leave her to die?

293
00:11:50,679 --> 00:11:52,399
We're just... just traveling together.

294
00:11:53,399 --> 00:11:55,360
That's all?

295
00:11:55,360 --> 00:11:58,000
From the way Xiaojiu looks at you...

296
00:11:58,559 --> 00:11:59,360
Changsheng,

297
00:12:00,240 --> 00:12:01,720
since when did you get so nosy?

298
00:12:02,440 --> 00:12:04,759
Sorry, Master. I shouldn't have asked.

299
00:12:04,759 --> 00:12:05,279
Master,

300
00:12:05,279 --> 00:12:07,440
did your master finally pass
the Formless Sea of Qi on to you?

301
00:12:10,720 --> 00:12:11,519
Your dantian

302
00:12:12,000 --> 00:12:12,879
is as lifeless as stone.

303
00:12:12,879 --> 00:12:14,120
It can't gather qi.

304
00:12:14,480 --> 00:12:16,279
You can't practice

305
00:12:16,279 --> 00:12:17,440
even the most basic
inner force technique.

306
00:12:18,080 --> 00:12:20,120
Your body simply
isn't capable of cultivation.

307
00:12:21,080 --> 00:12:24,159
Master, you can do anything.

308
00:12:24,159 --> 00:12:25,159
You must know a way.

309
00:12:27,879 --> 00:12:29,759
Please have mercy

310
00:12:29,759 --> 00:12:31,639
and help your disciple!

311
00:12:31,639 --> 00:12:32,519
Go away.

312
00:12:33,039 --> 00:12:34,159
I can't help you.

313
00:12:35,799 --> 00:12:37,120
Fine. If you won't help me,

314
00:12:37,240 --> 00:12:38,919
I'll go outside right now
and tell everyone

315
00:12:39,360 --> 00:12:41,360
that Master bought a full-color book

316
00:12:41,360 --> 00:12:42,360
of racy pictures last month.

317
00:12:42,360 --> 00:12:44,159
It's still under his pillow!

318
00:12:44,159 --> 00:12:44,960
Everyone, come quick...

319
00:12:48,159 --> 00:12:49,720
You little brat!

320
00:12:49,799 --> 00:12:51,919
Didn't we agree
you'd keep that to yourself?

321
00:12:52,200 --> 00:12:53,039
Master,

322
00:12:53,720 --> 00:12:55,200
please help me.

323
00:12:55,200 --> 00:12:57,679
I'm begging you.

324
00:12:58,120 --> 00:12:58,600
All right, all right.

325
00:12:58,600 --> 00:12:59,519
You win.

326
00:13:00,159 --> 00:13:01,360
I'll help you.

327
00:13:02,039 --> 00:13:04,159
But let me warn you first.

328
00:13:04,639 --> 00:13:08,240
Whether this works
is entirely up to you.

329
00:13:14,519 --> 00:13:17,440
The Daoist texts say you have to break

330
00:13:17,440 --> 00:13:18,840
before you can rebuild.

331
00:13:19,120 --> 00:13:21,399
I'll use the Marrow Cleansing Scripture

332
00:13:21,399 --> 00:13:23,519
to break open
your dantian and sea of qi,

333
00:13:23,600 --> 00:13:26,799
then rebuild your inner core.

334
00:13:29,279 --> 00:13:30,720
(From this day forward,)

335
00:13:30,720 --> 00:13:34,840
(your meridians, flesh, sinews, and
bones will all serve as your sea of qi,)

336
00:13:35,639 --> 00:13:37,879
(and hold power beyond measure.)

337
00:13:38,080 --> 00:13:41,919
(Does that mean I can finally
practice inner force?)

338
00:13:42,639 --> 00:13:45,360
(After the cleansing,
your sea of qi will be empty.)

339
00:13:45,360 --> 00:13:48,480
(Ordinary inner force techniques
won't do you any good.)

340
00:13:48,799 --> 00:13:49,960
(However,)

341
00:13:50,120 --> 00:13:51,320
(our sect's founder)

342
00:13:51,320 --> 00:13:53,679
(left behind a unique
inner force technique.)

343
00:13:53,679 --> 00:13:56,519
(It happens to suit
your body perfectly.)

344
00:14:04,519 --> 00:14:07,320
Master, what's it called?

345
00:14:07,759 --> 00:14:10,759
The Formless Sea of Qi.

346
00:14:11,200 --> 00:14:13,519
(From then on, your cultivation)

347
00:14:13,519 --> 00:14:15,960
(will progress
far faster than anyone else's.)

348
00:14:15,960 --> 00:14:16,960
(But remember,)

349
00:14:16,960 --> 00:14:18,360
(never use it)

350
00:14:18,360 --> 00:14:19,639
(unless you have no other choice.)

351
00:14:27,100 --> 00:14:27,580
♪Come on♪

352
00:14:31,100 --> 00:14:32,780
♪This battle, I won't retreat♪

353
00:14:34,740 --> 00:14:37,700
♪In worn-out clothes,
my hem still carries frost and dust♪

354
00:14:37,980 --> 00:14:40,900
♪Among the crowd,
who is laughing at my absurdity?♪

355
00:14:41,140 --> 00:14:43,980
♪They say my birth
has already decided my path♪

356
00:14:44,380 --> 00:14:46,980
♪But I refuse
to believe my birth decides my worth♪

357
00:14:47,500 --> 00:14:50,460
♪With one blade in hand,
I've weathered countless storms♪

358
00:14:50,700 --> 00:14:53,700
♪Covered in scars,
only to be called young and reckless♪

359
00:14:53,860 --> 00:14:56,780
♪If this world only bows
to status and bloodlines♪

360
00:14:56,940 --> 00:14:59,700
♪Then I'll break every rule
with a single slash♪

361
00:15:00,260 --> 00:15:03,580
♪Listen, this heartbeat echoes♪

362
00:15:03,620 --> 00:15:06,620
♪Fate is nothing but a net♪

363
00:15:06,660 --> 00:15:12,300
♪Either be trapped by it
or tear it apart♪

364
00:15:12,700 --> 00:15:14,740
♪I rise against fate and fight♪

365
00:15:15,300 --> 00:15:17,820
♪I don't believe
anyone is born above another♪

366
00:15:18,540 --> 00:15:20,940
♪Even this mortal body
dares to fight back♪

367
00:15:21,060 --> 00:15:24,740
♪I'll step on fate and grow beyond it♪

368
00:15:25,340 --> 00:15:27,460
♪I rise against fate and fight♪

369
00:15:28,380 --> 00:15:30,500
♪Even if the world's cold stares
stand in my way♪

370
00:15:30,660 --> 00:15:33,940
♪This blade will cut through
all worldly judgment♪

371
00:15:33,980 --> 00:15:38,260
♪I am my own king♪

372
00:15:51,340 --> 00:15:52,900
♪I emerge into the world♪

373
00:15:52,900 --> 00:15:54,660
♪Unknown, yet I dare
to shake the martial world♪

374
00:15:54,660 --> 00:15:56,020
♪My pride is my trump card♪

375
00:15:56,020 --> 00:15:57,820
♪Even if fate treats me as worthless,
I refuse to yield♪

376
00:15:57,820 --> 00:15:59,220
♪Born with a gift, I won't give in♪

377
00:15:59,220 --> 00:16:00,980
♪Against heaven's will,
I'll bet on my rise♪

378
00:16:00,980 --> 00:16:02,500
♪A sword in hand,
fresh out of the mountain♪

379
00:16:02,500 --> 00:16:04,220
♪I dare to break every rule♪

380
00:16:04,220 --> 00:16:05,540
♪I see through
the masks of human hearts♪

381
00:16:05,540 --> 00:16:07,380
♪Famous clans are nothing
but a few layers of disguise♪

382
00:16:07,380 --> 00:16:08,620
♪They kneel and beg for fame♪

383
00:16:08,620 --> 00:16:10,860
♪I stand and fight for my dignity♪

384
00:16:10,860 --> 00:16:12,380
♪Facing powerful foes, I will not bow♪

385
00:16:12,380 --> 00:16:13,980
♪With my blade in hand,
I decide what is right♪

386
00:16:13,980 --> 00:16:15,580
♪Stand for justice and never step back♪

387
00:16:15,580 --> 00:16:17,300
♪Even if the whole world
stands against me♪

388
00:16:17,300 --> 00:16:19,020
♪Untamed,
frost has carved me to the bone♪

389
00:16:19,020 --> 00:16:20,380
♪Only then do I become more like myself♪

390
00:16:20,380 --> 00:16:22,020
♪Fight, this life of mine is unyielding♪

391
00:16:22,020 --> 00:16:23,500
♪No matter how dark the martial world,
I'll walk through it♪

392
00:16:23,500 --> 00:16:25,220
♪For love, I do not fight for the world♪

393
00:16:25,220 --> 00:16:26,820
♪I only want
to protect her for a lifetime♪

394
00:16:26,820 --> 00:16:28,380
♪Carefree,
this fleeting life is but a brief stay♪

395
00:16:28,380 --> 00:16:32,700
♪Now I know all things can be overcome♪

396
00:16:32,700 --> 00:16:34,860
♪I raise my blade and change my fate♪

397
00:16:34,860 --> 00:16:37,460
♪Let me write the legend♪

398
00:16:42,340 --> 00:16:44,900
♪I rise against fate and fight♪

399
00:16:44,900 --> 00:16:48,220
♪Win or lose, strong or weak,
none of it matters to me♪

400
00:16:48,220 --> 00:16:50,700
♪Even if I fall, I will still shine♪

401
00:16:50,700 --> 00:16:54,780
♪Let my name
be carved into the vast world♪

402
00:16:55,140 --> 00:16:57,740
♪I rise against fate and fight♪

403
00:16:57,860 --> 00:17:00,220
♪If this world refuses to forgive me♪

404
00:17:00,220 --> 00:17:03,260
♪Then I'll burn away
all my edge and brilliance♪

405
00:17:03,260 --> 00:17:08,300
♪And trade it for a new dawn♪
